Box 258: Framed "Whole Wheat Sponge" collage of naked ladies inscribed to Griffin
              (1982). Also in Box 258 are five color facsimiles of paintings and collages by Tony
              Scibella. Possible titles of these include: I am The Loser (1998); Simone #6 (1999);
              Wonderly (1999); it's odds on that u lose...I will go to the track forever (1999);
              Don't Forget, Don't Ever Forget (1999).
